<p>In all, the Department has over 100 PhD scholars, and over 40 ME students during 2020-22. The Materials stream in the UG program has 19 students in the Class of 2019 and 15 in the Class of 2020.</p>

<p>The Department also hosts a fairly large number of post-graduate students and research scholars who visit us under the UGC-funded Networking Resource Centre for Materials (NRC-M) program. In addition, it also hosts a number of undergraduate and post-graduate students as summer interns.</p>

